description: Representing both the local food movement and the preservation of traditional cuisine, El Porteño’s empanadas will send those familiar with this Argentine staple on a trip down memory lane. Each buttery and flaky bite evokes the sights and sounds of Buenos Aires. Fusing family recipes of generations past with the best local and organic ingredients available, these handheld pies have Argentine expats and local devotees line up side by side outside this San Francisco food truck!
name: El Porteño
